    所有已实现的接口:
    GraphAnalytic<K,VV,EV,TriadicCensus.Result>

    public class TriadicCensus<K extends java.lang.Comparable<K> & CopyableValue<K>,VV,EV>
extends GraphAnalyticBase<K,VV,EV,TriadicCensus.Result>
    A triad is formed by three connected or unconnected vertices in a graph. The triadic census counts the occurrences of each type of triad.

    See http://vlado.fmf.uni-lj.si/pub/networks/doc/triads/triads.pdf
